WEBVTT

00:02:58.863 --> 00:03:01.204
if you unplug it for a few minutes --

00:03:01.228 --> 00:03:03.923
(Laughter)

00:03:03.947 --> 00:03:07.229
(Applause)

00:03:07.253 --> 00:03:08.976
including you.

00:03:10.975 --> 00:03:14.213
Three: there is almost
nothing outside of you

00:03:14.237 --> 00:03:17.149
that will help in any kind of lasting way,

00:03:17.173 --> 00:03:19.137
unless you're waiting for an organ.

00:03:19.958 --> 00:03:24.896
You can't buy, achieve or date
serenity and peace of mind.

00:03:24.920 --> 00:03:28.694
This is the most horrible truth,
and I so resent it.

00:03:29.549 --> 00:03:31.773
But it's an inside job,